  • Method Details

    • getPreDrillEntryDate

      public Date getPreDrillEntryDate()
      Return the pre drill entry date of this wellbore.

      Sodir description:
      Date when the predrilling activity of the wellbore started (see also Entry date).

      datetime, corresponds to the Sodir property wlbEntryPreDrillDate.

      Returns:
      Pre drill entry date of this wellbore. Null if not specified.

    • getPreDrillCompletionDate

      public Date getPreDrillCompletionDate()
      Return the pre drill completion date of this wellbore.

      Sodir description:
      Date when the predrilling activity of the wellbore was completed (see also completion date).

      datetime, corresponds to the Sodir property wlbCompPreDrillDate.

      Returns:
      Pre drill completion date of this wellbore. Null if not specified.

    • getProductionFacility

      public String getProductionFacility()
      Return production facility of this wellbore.

      Sodir description:
      The Sodir's name for the production facility, for development wells.

      varchar(50), corresponds to the Sodir property wlbProductionFacility.

      Returns:
      Production facility of this wellbore.

    • getContentPlanned

      public String getContentPlanned()
      Return planned content of this wellbore.

      Sodir description:
      Only relevant for development wellbores, planned type of produced or injected fluid.
      Examples of legal values:

      • CO2
      • CUTTINGS
      • GAS
      • NOT APPLICABLE
      • NOT AVAILABLE
      • WATER
      • WATER/GAS

      varchar(40), corresponds to the Sodir property wlbContentPlanned.

      Returns:
      Planned content of this wellbore.

    • getNpdidFacilityProducing

      public String getNpdidFacilityProducing()
      Return ID of the producing facility of this wellbore.

      Sodir description:
      Sodir's unique id for the production facility, for development wellbores.

      bigint, corresponds to the Sodir property fclNpdidFacilityProducing.

      Returns:
      ID of the producing facility of this wellbore.

    • getNpdidTargetProductionLicense

      public String getNpdidTargetProductionLicense()
      Return ID of the target production license.

      Sodir description:
      NPDID production license target. Sodir unique key for the production license of the wellbore target. This can be another production license then where the wellhead position.

      int, corresponds to the Sodir property prlNpdidProdLicenceTarget.

      Returns:
      ID of the target production license. Null if N/A.
